if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe5857d1a485b56880af899bc6c938cefaffc67","tid":339500,"uid":57486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"釣新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adcff30c78dbc4ddb80dc401642ff44ed32175c","tid":339500,"uid":44711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"又回帶"},{"pid":"386f98b76d2bae37644c239ccb2011b7811a146c","tid":339500,"uid":39780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>釣新會然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e969ccc85387179483932aac2b60c313154f3b8","tid":339500,"uid":4586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"依個笑話令我好感觸，<br />\n<br />\n當我第一次睇既時候自己重係讀緊中學，<br />\n<br />\n自以為有一班好好既「朋友」，自己又有少少小聰明，<br />\n<br />\n每日番學放學都有一大班人陪著自己咁，<br />\n<br />\n每次同同學去行旺角、打波、食下野都覺得好開心，<br />\n<br />\n結果中學畢業之後，<br />\n<br />\n全部既「朋友」都選擇左升學，有IVE有海外，<br />\n<br />\n結果本身所謂既「朋友」再無搵自己，<br />\n<br />\n自己有試過主動打俾佢地，問人出唔出黎行下，<br />\n<br />\n答案好多都係「下，邊個邊個黎唔黎」、「要溫書喎」，<br />\n<br />\n結果好快就再無人記得我。<br />\n<br />\n畢業至今已經有十年，<br />\n<br />\n拍過一次拖四年，一次拖一個月，<br />\n<br />\n四年既係一個好珍惜自己同埋好傻既女仔，<br />\n<br />\n一個月果個次係貪新鮮當我玩具咁既人，<br />\n<br />\n曾經戶口有過二三十萬儲款，<br />\n<br />\n依家已經無晒，<br />\n<br />\n依十年，自己到底睇倒幾多，改變左幾多？<br />\n<br />\n多謝樓主分享